{"tid":2328048,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳帆：無計劃考慮提高居屋交樓標準","createTime":"2020-12-16T10:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T13:43:30.000Z","uid":268272,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7a27455385a6ed752dddb43a87d89533dfb37e49","tid":2328048,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:52:43.000Z","msg":"自2014年起推出的新居屋被批評跟現行公屋規格無異，在長遠房屋策略周年報告，有記者問及相關問題。不過運輸及房屋局局長陳帆表明在目前土地供應、考慮成本效應及節約原則下，加上申請反應理想，無計劃考慮提高居屋交樓標準，希望市民能多諒解。而過往經驗顯示，不少搬入家庭均願意花錢裝修，按個人喜好建造「舒適的家」，故房委會一切從簡，配套上簡易處理，是基於環保經濟效益考量。<br />\n<br />\n而綠置居及公屋屬旋轉門，估不會作間格和設計區別。"},{"pid":"a95af97111ecbe390ae44f0227bd2ad602f3df2f","tid":2328048,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:53:15.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2830105/%E3%80%90%E5%B1%85%E5%B1%8B2020%E3%80%91%E6%88%BF%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E4%BB%A5%E6%B8%85%E6%B0%B4%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%98%E3%80%80%E9%99%B3%E5%B8%86%EF%BC%9A%E8%AE%93%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E7%B2%89%E9%A3%BE%E6%96%B0%E5%B1%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2830105%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%25B1%258B2020%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25A8%2593%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E4%25BB%2598%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25B8%2586%25EF%25BC%259A%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%25B2%2589%25E9%25A3%25BE%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B1%2585&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE12%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=9f31077d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2830105/%E3%80%90%E5%B1%85%E5%B1%8B2020%E3%80%91%E6%88%BF%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E4%BB%A5%E6%B8%85%E6%B0%B4%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%A4%E4%BB%98%E3%80%80%E9%99%B3%E5%B8%86%EF%BC%9A%E8%AE%93%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E7%B2%89%E9%A3%BE%E6%96%B0%E5%B1%85</a>"},{"pid":"fd7d2940bbc2613dadfc47677700fab62fa1a153","tid":2328048,"uid":268272,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"reply